item.title: CVE-2023-1427|2024-08-02T05:49:11.507Z -- unknown -- photo%20gallery%20by%2010web
item.description: - The Photo Gallery by 10Web WordPress plugin before 1.8.15 did not ensure that uploaded files are kept inside its uploads folder, allowing high privilege users to put images anywhere in the filesystem via a path traversal vector.
